hysician asap, I am just a medical student. Hope it helps!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T20:13:46.000Z","msg":"係咪真係讀medical school .......<br />\nPulse 同 Blood pressure 都未分清<br />\n人地講緊radial-radial delay, 左右手pulse唔同<br />\n你就講左右手blood pressure(interarm bp difference ) 唔同 ......."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T23:20:32.000Z","msg":"都有可能係主動脈剝離？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:39:07.000Z","msg":"係，無論2隻手pulse唔同 定 2隻手blood pressure 都有一個可能係 主動脈剝離，<br />\n有就點同要即刻睇心內<br />\n<br />\n樓上話咩smart watch 度pulse唔準個d就晒氣。 樓主一隻手摸家人左手pulse, 另一隻手同時摸右手pulse, 唔同步就知係咪真係radial-radial delay<br />\n<br />\nAortic dissection 的risk factors都叫中唔少<br />\nOld male+  afib +/- 高血壓/糖尿，雖然無好classical的severe abdominal/chest pain radiating to the back, 但atypical presentation 都講唔埋<br />\n<br />\n主要係而家 afib 底 唔食藥 rate control無做，anticoagulants又無 仲要跑步<br />\n有無radial radial delay都隨時就冧低瓜得或者中風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b766549906bb0b225c9bb573ec9dee1c22a70d","tid":2333333,"uid":79823,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"971e5012a55b515b2544e3dee90dd53116c68d20","tid":2333333,"uid":381001,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af15b37b31d00e2bd1f459c8b3ec2b76511243af","tid":2333333,"uid":79823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T23:25:33.000Z","msg":"恕我無知<br />\n未聽過一隻病會左右手pulse唔同<br />\n<br />\n建議量2隻手血壓睇下點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:19:39.000Z","msg":"咁你真係幾無知<br />\n兩隻手pulse唔到又有(Radial-radial delay)<br />\n手同大脾pulse唔同又有( radial-femoral delay )"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T02:11:24.000Z","msg":"依家人地話有把脈話有delay?<br />\n人地primary issue 係兩隻手pulse rate 唔同<br />\n係你自己先入為主喎 <br />\nClinical world 最忌就係呢d<br />\n<br />\n每次呢d post 都一定有呢d 傻鳩認屎認屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e228c60f56869f5143d340f6951be4ad83581976","tid":2333333,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"三大問題 血壓~130<br />\nPulse&gt;100<br />\n心臟纖顫<br />\n左右手pulse 差40 點確認緊<br />\n唉<br />\n寧願隨時中風都唔食藥"}}